{"tid":1531741,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"呢場仗大家想卑鄙咁贏 定係 好正氣咁贏先","createTime":"2019-09-02T10:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T07:40:44.000Z","uid":88032,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1753a2bd5c805143d4c09b6068d3c5bc60f805c3","tid":1531741,"uid":88032,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:19:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>大家可以學何君堯送生果/飯/飲品比黑警，你懂的</strong></span>"},{"pid":"03a4fd23d888c285334867f0a0aae9ec4fea47d6","tid":1531741,"uid":60049,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:20:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b517425da5778eeb924f529daa78bebb45dab3","tid":1531741,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:21:21.000Z","msg":"[置頂] 建議9月8日百萬人大遊行/集會，請求美國國會通過人權及民主法案<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1530650\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1530650</a><br />\n<br />\n901 機場測試係成功<br />\n辛苦曬行左20公里既手足 勿被帶風向<br />\n<br />\n908 我希望美國巴絲手足都有遊行<br />\n聲援香港同埋同要請求美國國會通過人權法!<br />\n<br />\n908 建議：<br />\n大量英文文宣/紙牌<br />\n高舉大量美國議員大頭相<br />\n(睇下邊個出過聲又重要既)<br />\n高舉大量國旗<br />\n唔建議勇武，因為主題涉及美國<br />\n(另一原因係 廢時佢又區區有狗搜身兼<br />\n補充文具需時又珍貴)<br />\n領事館門前唱國歌<br />\n無人申請不反 都要照上街<br />\n<br />\n需要文宣制圖 然後我幫你宣傳<br />\n由今日開始宣! 908照上街!<br />\n<br />\n建議內容copy某位巴打既<br />\n9月我要照上街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c896dc09de9c71d468069ea7c1da23268835793","tid":1531741,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T10:21:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"> US Congress will be resumed on 9/9!</span></span><br />\